        Łsarvaṃ ca tam arthaṃ vidhāya brāhmaṇo 'ntaradhīyata$ ||154||
        Łtasya rājarṣer vidhātā tenaiva veṣeṇa parīkṣārtham āgata iti$ ||155||.<sep/></NOTE>

